<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>256</hymn_number>
<author>Rev. K. Thuomngel</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa chu chawian hitiu,
 A lungsietna I muh u hin;
 Thilsiem chengin,
 Amah chawihatna la sau hen la,
 Ei khawtuohna a let ziekin.

[V2]
 Lungsietna thilpiek, thaithak kipah um,
 Kipahna la sa'n lawm hitiu;
 Aman guoh zu, nisa, khawlum leh khaw vawt,
 Thaichi gahna dinga ei piek ziekin;
 Chawih-atin um hen, chawih-atin um hen, um hen.
 Chawih-atin um hen, Amen.

[V3]
 2. Thaichi chu I va tuh a,
 Hih theih dang bangmah I nei puoi;
 Mah leh Lalpa
 Hatna a etkawla umin tun,
 Thaithak kipahum I mu tau.

[V4]
 3. Mel muh loh ginna mita
 Ena sawttak hai bang I ngak;
 Lalpa lungsietna vanga-
 Etkawla um in tun,
 Thaithak sakmel I mu tau ie.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa, ka hun chawian ui,
 Na lungsietna ka muh u hin;
 Ka pawihmawh chenguh Nangin,
 Nei ngaihtuoh sak zela,
 Chawih-atin um zing ta'n, Amen.</lyrics>
<title>Lungsiet Na Thilpiek</title>
</song>